'''FNV-23-B''' was the antiviral drug developed to "counteract" [[FNV-23]], or the Gray Death, the plague that struck the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Sedesia]]. This cure was also created by the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]], and every dose contained tiny globules of FNV-23 held within a polysaccharide coating. When digested, it released a new strain of FNV-23 into the system, thereby requiring another dose of the "cure."

